response.original_title: Under the Caresses of the Martinet
response.overview: One of the rarest (and most cheerful) S&M films ever made. "Sous Les Caresses du Martinet" (Under the Caresses of the Martinet) features two nice girls who make sado-masochism look as innocent and adorable as a pillow fight. The attitude is playful, consensual, and very French.
